    "The results of hyperparameter tuning indicate that small models can also show great performances given the limited number of data we have.",
    "We design a systematic evaluation scheme for polymer generation with multiple metrics, and leverage it to comprehensively evaluate the generation tasks.",
    "Given the positive and negative correlations between these metrics, we further examine the model performance in a multi-objective setup.",
    "Moreover, by conditioning the generative process, our models are capable of producing polymers tailored to specific target properties.",
    "Empowered by our proposed approach, the generation of novel, unique, chemically valid, and potentially synthesizable polymers can be accomplished in microseconds."
